As far as i know there are three types of ntr : 

1.- Netorare : The protagonist gets his/her love interest stolen from him/her
2.- Netori : The protagonist steals the love interest of someone else
3.- Netorase : There is a couple and one of them (may or may not be the protagonist) gets his/her partner to engage in sexual activities with other people (this type of ntr generally evolves to netorare)

Here you are seeing Netori.

Thing is this site lumps together the three different types of ntr into the same tag ‘Netorare’, which is a problem, but well, I don’t think there’s anything we can do about that.
